results.deck: Midas Interactive is a British publisher focused on budget titles.
results.description:
Midas Interactive has published games for the PS2, PSP, Nintendo DS, Nintendo Wii and PC, including games such as Mr. Driller for the Dreamcast, and WWII: Battle Over the Pacific for the Playstation 2. It has been less active in recent years, mainly focusing on rerelasing its catalog on current platforms.

Midas is part of the Majesty House group, alongside Ghostlight and Laughing Jackal.
